data.description: No projects here! This renovated 3-bedroom home is tucked away on a quiet street in Deltona, just minutes from everything.    When you walk in the front door, you’ll find a modern open floorplan with lots of natural light and LVP flooring throughout (no carpets here!).    The gorgeous kitchen features granite countertops, 42-inch cabinets, a subway-tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast nook, and an expansive breakfast bar overlooking the living room.    The isolated primary bedroom includes a spacious ensuite with plenty of storage, while the guest rooms share the full bathroom at the end of the hall. Don’t forget about the clever laundry area and all the storage in the attached garage.    In the massive backyard, there’s plenty of room for a patio, fire pit, garden, or future pool. The lot faces a forest both in the front and at the back – creating lots of privacy.    This serene neighborhood is ideally located close to parks, schools, and numerous lakes. Dupont Lakes Center (Publix/Lowe’s/restaurants) and I-4 are just 5 mins from your front door, and you can be at the beach in about half an hour!
